00:39:15.100 --> 00:39:18.470
that point to the fact that the opportunities

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:21.950
of Russian manufacturers associated

00:39:21.960 --> 00:39:24.230
with increasing their competitiveness

00:39:24.240 --> 00:39:26.970
in the market will be related

00:39:26.980 --> 00:39:29.390
to the fact that within the framework

00:39:29.400 --> 00:39:31.570
of the World Trade Organization

00:39:31.580 --> 00:39:32.750
they will be able to enter

00:39:32.760 --> 00:39:36.370
the general system of preferences

00:39:36.380 --> 00:39:39.050
and the system of non-

00:39:39.060 --> 00:39:40.570
discrimination.

