The next thing I would like to draw

00:39:56.120 --> 00:39:58.850
your attention to is the country

00:39:58.860 --> 00:40:01.010
orientation of Russian foreign trade

00:40:01.020 --> 00:40:06.150
based on two blocs of countries, namely

00:40:06.160 --> 00:40:08.530
the countries of the near and abroad,

00:40:08.540 --> 00:40:10.870
or the countries of the CIS and

00:40:10.880 --> 00:40:15.730
the countries of the far abroad,

00:40:15.740 --> 00:40:19.190
that is, predominantly developed

00:40:19.200 --> 00:40:20.690
countries.

00:40:20.700 --> 00:40:23.170
Please note that, in general,

00:40:23.180 --> 00:40:25.090
of course, the chart shows

00:40:25.100 --> 00:40:28.070
on the chart that Russian exports

00:40:28.080 --> 00:40:31.050
are constantly growing and

00:40:31.060 --> 00:40:34.230
continue to grow in 2003-2005.

00:40:34.530 --> 00:40:37.170
What is the proportion of near

00:40:37.180 --> 00:40:38.490
and far abroad?

00:40:38.890 --> 00:40:40.870
The share of the near abroad is fairly

00:40:40.880 --> 00:40:44.230
stable and the growth is quite small.

00:40:44.310 --> 00:40:47.270
But the share of far abroad, just outside

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:52.530
the CIS countries, it simply, for

00:40:52.540 --> 00:40:54.190
example, jumped sharply in the

00:40:54.200 --> 00:40:57.450
period between 2003 - 2005 and

00:40:57.460 --> 00:40:58.930
continues to grow now.

00:40:59.550 --> 00:41:00.830
This is not only due to the

00:41:00.840 --> 00:41:03.950
energy consumption in these countries,

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:06.390
it is due to the overall level of

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:09.330
income and development in these countries.

00:41:09.390 --> 00:41:11.170
The richer the economy, as we have

00:41:11.180 --> 00:41:12.290
learned in the course

00:41:12.300 --> 00:41:13.550
of international economic relations,

00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:16.110
the more opportunities and capabilities

00:41:16.120 --> 00:41:17.730
they have to participate

00:41:17.740 --> 00:41:19.410
with our country in international

00:41:19.420 --> 00:41:21.550
trade.

00:41:21.560 --> 00:41:23.990
Certainly the CIS countries, apparently,

00:41:24.000 --> 00:41:28.250
after going through the path of market

00:41:28.260 --> 00:41:32.770
transformations, I hope to increase the

00:41:32.780 --> 00:41:35.270
level of their income and then they will

00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:41.670
also become the object of mutual

00:41:41.680 --> 00:41:45.710
flows between Russia and the near abroad.

00:41:45.750 --> 00:41:47.650
Moreover, we are connected

00:41:47.660 --> 00:41:50.090
by quite large historical traditions

00:41:50.100 --> 00:41:54.270
and although over the past 15-17 years

00:41:54.280 --> 00:41:58.430
our production has learned to live

00:41:58.440 --> 00:42:00.290
independently and separately, but

00:42:02.450 --> 00:42:05.470
nevertheless, as soon as the

00:42:05.480 --> 00:42:08.070
crisis situation in these countries

