And that is why the

00:43:19.420 --> 00:43:22.990
competitiveness of the products offered

00:43:23.000 --> 00:43:25.050
from developed countries is much higher

00:43:25.060 --> 00:43:28.070
than from the countries of the

00:43:28.080 --> 00:43:30.250
former socialist community.

