first of all, to the economic

00:46:07.880 --> 00:46:10.210
growth in Russia, which has been

00:46:10.220 --> 00:46:13.090
recorded since 2004.

00:46:13.690 --> 00:46:15.970
Within the framework of economic theory

00:46:15.980 --> 00:46:17.610
it has always been proven that as

00:46:17.620 --> 00:46:19.990
soon as the gross domestic product of

00:46:20.000 --> 00:46:22.390
the country begins to grow, not only

00:46:27.200 --> 00:46:31.310
is the internal confirmation of the axiom

00:46:31.320 --> 00:46:33.950
of the theory of international economic

00:46:33.960 --> 00:46:36.410
relations manifested in

00:46:36.420 --> 00:46:38.010
the external economic

00:46:38.020 --> 00:46:40.450
indicators of Russia growing.

00:46:41.330 --> 00:46:43.450
So, with the growth of income,

00:46:43.460 --> 00:46:46.390
our end consumers and, most

00:46:46.400 --> 00:46:48.810
importantly, our producers

00:46:48.820 --> 00:46:53.030
agree to buy a larger share

00:46:53.040 --> 00:46:55.250
of imported products in order

00:46:55.870 --> 00:46:57.890
to raise both their standard

00:46:57.900 --> 00:47:00.470
of living and to upgrade

00:47:00.480 --> 00:47:03.630
the production that should

00:47:03.640 --> 00:47:06.150
be more competitive.

00:47:06.470 --> 00:47:08.390
Another factor that affects the fact

00:47:08.400 --> 00:47:12.090
that, since 2004, the foreign trade

00:47:12.550 --> 00:47:15.950
saldo has become negative in Russia

00:47:15.960 --> 00:47:19.310
is related to the fact that the Russian

00:47:19.320 --> 00:47:25.150
ruble rate is increasing methodically.

00:47:25.990 --> 00:47:29.010
Despite the intervention that the Central

00:47:29.020 --> 00:47:31.010
Bank regularly conducts on the currency

00:47:31.020 --> 00:47:33.570
market, it is still not possible

00:47:33.580 --> 00:47:36.510
to reduce the exchange rate

00:47:36.520 --> 00:47:39.010
sharply enough.

00:47:39.020 --> 00:47:43.910
We considered that if the currency

00:47:43.920 --> 00:47:46.750
rate of a country increases, it

00:47:46.760 --> 00:47:48.670
will one way or another lead

00:47:48.680 --> 00:47:50.990
to a trend of decreasing exports

00:47:51.000 --> 00:47:57.890
and increasing imports.

00:47:57.910 --> 00:47:58.290
Why is?

00:47:58.370 --> 00:48:00.250
Because the ruble is becoming more

00:48:00.260 --> 00:48:02.470
expensive, and now we can

00:48:02.480 --> 00:48:04.130
exchange more foreign currency

00:48:04.140 --> 00:48:07.870
for a more stable, expensive ruble

00:48:07.880 --> 00:48:10.050
and, accordingly, buy more

00:48:10.060 --> 00:48:11.510
imported goods.

00:48:11.710 --> 00:48:13.050
On the contrary, the foreign

00:48:13.060 --> 00:48:16.010
consumer of Russian exports is facing

00:48:16.020 --> 00:48:18.730
a situation where the goods offered

00:48:18.740 --> 00:48:21.130
by Russian production have not

00:48:21.140 --> 00:48:24.710
only increased in connection with

00:48:24.720 --> 00:48:26.750
the increase in global prices,

00:48:26.760 --> 00:48:27.470
I mean energy, but

00:48:27.480 --> 00:48:29.570
in principle other groups

00:48:29.580 --> 00:48:32.390
of export products have increased

00:48:32.400 --> 00:48:35.430
precisely because now in

00:48:35.440 --> 00:48:37.850
order to buy this goods at the

00:48:37.860 --> 00:48:41.230
same price, you need to

00:48:41.240 --> 00:48:43.890
exchange more euros or

00:48:43.900 --> 00:48:45.470
dollars for rubles.

00:48:45.550 --> 00:48:47.190
This leads to a relative increase in

00:48:47.200 --> 00:48:48.410
the price of goods.

00:48:48.910 --> 00:48:53.330
This situation is also known

00:48:53.340 --> 00:48:55.570
to Europe, where Europeans

00:48:55.580 --> 00:48:57.750
are not satisfied with the rise

00:48:57.760 --> 00:49:00.030
of the euro against the US dollar,

00:49:00.040 --> 00:49:01.890
and they even calculated how many

00:49:01.900 --> 00:49:03.650
millions of euros they lost

00:49:03.660 --> 00:49:05.750
there simply from the six-month

00:49:05.760 --> 00:49:09.000
rise of the US dollar.

00:49:09.000 --> 00:49:12.260
But I want to draw your attention to the fact

00:49:12.500 --> 00:49:15.040
that during this period of time, 2006-2007,

00:49:15.050 --> 00:49:19.220
the rise in the ruble is not only associated

00:49:19.230 --> 00:49:22.380
with the growth of our exports, it is

00:49:22.390 --> 00:49:25.480
associated with the huge influx of

00:49:25.490 --> 00:49:29.900
oil dollars and euros on the territory of

00:49:29.910 --> 00:49:33.400
Russia, it is also associated with the fact

00:49:33.410 --> 00:49:36.660
that the currencies of our foreign

00:49:36.670 --> 00:49:38.160
partners, in particular the United States,

00:49:38.170 --> 00:49:40.640
are subject to fluctuation.

00:49:41.900 --> 00:49:45.200
The period 2006-2005 was marked by

00:49:45.210 --> 00:49:47.240
the fact that in this period of

00:49:47.250 --> 00:49:49.360
time the dollar rate was steadily

00:49:49.370 --> 00:49:50.540
declining.

00:49:50.960 --> 00:49:52.200
On the one hand, the Americans

00:49:52.210 --> 00:49:54.580
just got export gains from such

00:49:54.590 --> 00:49:57.440
a reduction in the ruble rate

00:49:57.450 --> 00:49:59.940
and slightly improved their payment

00:49:59.950 --> 00:50:02.120
and trade balance.

00:50:02.360 --> 00:50:06.400
The US partners, Russia,

00:50:06.410 --> 00:50:08.080
should have suffered

00:50:08.090 --> 00:50:10.740
from this situation.

00:50:11.160 --> 00:50:12.900
As you can see from the table,

00:50:12.910 --> 00:50:14.900
I will repeat again, our net

00:50:14.910 --> 00:50:17.320
exports increased in negative,

00:50:17.340 --> 00:50:21.620
it became unbalanced.

00:50:21.630 --> 00:50:24.240
As the US market is changing in

00:50:24.250 --> 00:50:26.520
the stabilization of the dollar,

00:50:26.530 --> 00:50:28.860
this trend was already marked

00:50:28.870 --> 00:50:30.640
in 2007, when the US Central

00:50:30.650 --> 00:50:33.740
Bank has already raised the refinancing

00:50:33.750 --> 00:50:35.120
rate by a percentage

00:50:35.130 --> 00:50:39.560
point, which gives the

00:50:39.570 --> 00:50:43.480
opportunity to balance

00:50:43.490 --> 00:50:45.460
Russia’s foreign trade

00:50:45.470 --> 00:50:46.460
flows.

00:50:48.540 --> 00:50:50.700
As you can see, exports and imports

00:50:50.710 --> 00:50:52.200
are influenced by a large

00:50:52.210 --> 00:50:54.720
number of factors, both currency

00:50:54.730 --> 00:50:56.240
and demand.

