In terms of demand, I would like

00:50:58.290 --> 00:51:01.400
to point out that the growth of

00:51:01.410 --> 00:51:03.440
our exports will still depend on

00:51:03.450 --> 00:51:05.760
the growth of gross domestic

00:51:05.770 --> 00:51:07.220
product abroad.

00:51:07.460 --> 00:51:09.760
That is, as far as countries, the

00:51:09.770 --> 00:51:11.300
main consumers of our exports,

00:51:11.310 --> 00:51:13.560
I mean Western Europe, as you

00:51:13.570 --> 00:51:16.120
saw on the chart, is 60% of our

00:51:16.130 --> 00:51:18.940
exports, as far as Western

00:51:18.950 --> 00:51:22.080
Europe will maintain a stable

00:51:22.090 --> 00:51:24.040
economic growth, so much

00:51:24.460 --> 00:51:26.980
our goods in the Western

00:51:26.990 --> 00:51:28.460
European market will

00:51:28.470 --> 00:51:30.140
be in demand.

00:51:30.240 --> 00:51:32.500
If, God give it, their development

00:51:32.510 --> 00:51:34.700
is somehow disrupted and there is some

00:51:34.710 --> 00:51:37.500
economic decline, then our exports

00:51:37.510 --> 00:51:39.540
may be reduced even more,

00:51:39.550 --> 00:51:42.020
and for us this will be an

00:51:42.030 --> 00:51:43.580
unwanted situation.

00:51:43.840 --> 00:51:45.880
From my example, you can see

00:51:45.890 --> 00:51:47.440
how closely connected

00:51:47.450 --> 00:51:50.640
all countries in the world are

00:51:50.650 --> 00:51:52.520
by export and import flows.

00:51:52.720 --> 00:51:55.420
Therefore, in principle, the common

00:51:55.580 --> 00:51:57.880
prosperity of one country cannot be

00:51:57.890 --> 00:52:01.340
without the prosperity of neighbors

00:52:01.350 --> 00:52:04.420
and more distant neighbors, since these

00:52:04.430 --> 00:52:06.520
interrelated export-import flows

00:52:06.530 --> 00:52:09.540
raise the overall economic development

00:52:09.550 --> 00:52:12.760
of all countries in the world.

00:52:13.740 --> 00:52:17.060
Based on this, it is clear why the

00:52:17.070 --> 00:52:19.560
countries outside the World

00:52:19.570 --> 00:52:21.820
Trade Organization are trying

00:52:21.830 --> 00:52:24.880
to join this negotiating integration

00:52:24.890 --> 00:52:27.900
process and participate in the

