again.

00:53:58.820 --> 00:54:01.900
What are the objectives and objectives of Russia’

00:54:01.910 --> 00:54:03.940
s accession to the World Trade Organization?

00:54:04.440 --> 00:54:07.400
Of course, these goals can be

00:54:07.410 --> 00:54:09.560
formulated in connection with the

00:54:09.570 --> 00:54:11.900
benefits that any country that has

00:54:13.330 --> 00:54:16.000
become a member of the World

00:54:16.010 --> 00:54:17.800
Trade Organization receives.

00:54:18.520 --> 00:54:20.820
The first goal is to obtain

00:54:20.830 --> 00:54:22.680
non-discriminatory conditions

00:54:22.690 --> 00:54:24.720
for access to foreign markets

00:54:24.730 --> 00:54:27.540
for Russian products.

00:54:27.800 --> 00:54:29.760
As I have already given an example,

00:54:30.400 --> 00:54:31.740
there are quite strict rules

00:54:31.750 --> 00:54:33.840
of discrimination on a number

00:54:33.850 --> 00:54:36.120
of goods that are quite

00:54:36.130 --> 00:54:40.520
competitive in the world market.

00:54:41.000 --> 00:54:45.040
Furthermore, access to the mechanism

00:54:45.050 --> 00:54:49.760
for settling trade disputes, which

00:54:49.770 --> 00:54:52.600
is well-developed within

00:54:52.610 --> 00:54:54.580
the framework of the World Trade

00:54:54.590 --> 00:54:55.640
Organization, is very important

00:54:55.650 --> 00:54:57.980
for Russia and is not accidentally

00:54:57.990 --> 00:54:59.560
used by more and more

00:54:59.570 --> 00:55:03.040
WTO member countries.

00:55:03.820 --> 00:55:06.240
On the other hand, if we become

00:55:06.250 --> 00:55:09.140
members of the WTO, it means that

00:55:09.150 --> 00:55:11.140
in principle most countries

00:55:11.150 --> 00:55:13.640
in the world do not conflict

00:55:13.650 --> 00:55:16.280
with us on trade, commodity and other

00:55:16.360 --> 00:55:18.260
positions that fall within

00:55:18.380 --> 00:55:21.180
the jurisdiction of the WTO.

00:55:21.700 --> 00:55:24.000
Our foreign policy

00:55:24.010 --> 00:55:26.140
is becoming more

00:55:26.150 --> 00:55:28.360
predictable.

00:55:28.980 --> 00:55:32.660
When countries join the World Trade

00:55:32.670 --> 00:55:34.320
Organization, one of the requirements

00:55:34.330 --> 00:55:37.000
in the WTO process is the harmonization

00:55:37.010 --> 00:55:41.620
of domestic laws with WTO rules

00:55:41.630 --> 00:55:43.640
and norms, with international,

00:55:43.650 --> 00:55:45.840
so to speak, standards.

00:55:46.360 --> 00:55:47.700
International standards

00:55:47.710 --> 00:55:49.780
envisage the liberalization

00:55:49.940 --> 00:55:52.980
of domestic legislation in

00:55:52.990 --> 00:55:55.380
relation to foreign investors.

00:55:55.390 --> 00:55:57.380
Thus, creating a blatant

00:55:57.390 --> 00:55:58.980
clearing for investment is

00:55:58.990 --> 00:56:02.680
also one of the goals of Russia’

00:56:02.690 --> 00:56:04.340
s accession to the WTO.

00:56:05.340 --> 00:56:08.660
If you look at the statistics,

00:56:08.670 --> 00:56:11.280
investors have reacted

00:56:11.290 --> 00:56:13.860
very strongly to the fact that in

00:56:13.870 --> 00:56:17.240
2006-2007 Russia was facing

00:56:17.250 --> 00:56:19.980
a violent conviction with

00:56:19.990 --> 00:56:22.100
all conflicting countries

00:56:22.110 --> 00:56:24.360
or interested countries about

00:56:24.370 --> 00:56:25.600
joining the WTO.

00:56:25.880 --> 00:56:27.520
And we have an influx of foreign

00:56:27.530 --> 00:56:29.580
investment into Russia increased

00:56:29.590 --> 00:56:33.520
to almost 40% in the first

00:56:33.530 --> 00:56:36.600
quarter of 2007 compared to the

00:56:36.610 --> 00:56:39.880
first quarter of 2006.

00:56:40.180 --> 00:56:41.980
Why this happens?

00:56:42.360 --> 00:56:44.720
It appears that foreign investors

00:56:44.730 --> 00:56:46.840
are expecting Russia’s accession

00:56:46.850 --> 00:56:49.060
to the WTO and are trying to take

00:56:49.070 --> 00:56:50.540
positions in advance.

00:56:50.550 --> 00:56:52.740
There is also a flow of reinvestments.

00:56:52.750 --> 00:56:53.760


00:56:54.040 --> 00:56:56.500
When domestic producers who

00:56:56.510 --> 00:57:00.120
exported excess capital

00:57:00.130 --> 00:57:01.780
abroad because they saw less

00:57:02.520 --> 00:57:05.260
risky use of this capital

00:57:05.270 --> 00:57:07.800
on Russian territory,

00:57:07.810 --> 00:57:09.800
they were less likely to

00:57:09.810 --> 00:57:11.960
invest money abroad, this

00:57:11.970 --> 00:57:14.220
capital also begins to

00:57:14.230 --> 00:57:15.940
return to the Russian

00:57:15.950 --> 00:57:16.960
economy.

00:57:16.970 --> 00:57:19.640
This process began in 2003

00:57:19.650 --> 00:57:22.360
and continues to this day.

00:57:23.000 --> 00:57:26.500
Accordingly, the WTO membership

00:57:26.510 --> 00:57:29.040
will be a laxmuse paper,

00:57:29.100 --> 00:57:31.340
an indicator that will show

00:57:31.350 --> 00:57:33.380
foreign investors to

00:57:33.390 --> 00:57:35.120
come, invest, develop,

00:57:35.340 --> 00:57:36.840
organize and create new

00:57:36.850 --> 00:57:38.660
jobs on modern technologies

00:57:38.670 --> 00:57:40.700
in Russia.

