But note, even with this seemingly

00:57:50.090 --> 00:57:52.020
stormy growth, what figures can

00:57:52.030 --> 00:57:54.060
we give – 10, 20, 30 percent growth

00:57:54.070 --> 00:57:56.640
over the last few years, nevertheless,

