the share of foreign investment

00:58:00.670 --> 00:58:02.240
in the total investment

00:58:02.250 --> 00:58:05.640
of the domestic economy

00:58:05.650 --> 00:58:07.420
is insignificant, that

00:58:07.430 --> 00:58:09.720
is, the percentage there rises

00:58:09.730 --> 00:58:12.120
slightly to 10 percent.

